Usage: setModuleView [-help] [[-topReadOnly {true false}] ] [{-hinst <string> | -partition <string>} -type {readOnly interface all} ]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
-hinst <string>                     # List of partition hinsts
                                    # (string, optional)
-partition <string>                 # List of partitions (string, optional)
-topReadOnly {true false}           # Mark top level as readOnly
                                    # (enum, optional)
-type {readOnly interface all}      # Partition view type (enum, optional)